<p>To speak with a criminal defense attorney at our firm, contact our law office in Coeur d'Alene, Idaho. We offer attorneys who are licensed to practice in state and federal courts in Idaho and Washington.</p>
<h2>Get the Strong Defense You Deserve</h2>
<p>We strongly believe that every person accused of a crime has a right to a zealous defense. Our team of attorneys includes former prosecutors and skilled trial lawyers who will provide the vigorous defense you require.</p>
<p>We understand that a criminal conviction of any kind is a serious matter which can significantly impact you and your family. Whether we are handling a case involving a simple traffic ticket or a high-level felony charge, we commit ourselves to providing the vigorous defense our clients deserve.</p>
<p>To ensure that our clients receive a strong defense, we carefully prepare each case for the possibility of trial. We examine police conduct leading to the arrest of our clients to determine if police errors may be used to the advantage of our clients. We analyze the prosecution's case thoroughly to identify potential defenses which may be available to our clients and to determine weaknesses in the prosecution's case.</p>
<p>By preparing each case for trial and building a strong defense, our objective is to put our clients in a better position to obtain a charge dismissal, an acquittal at trial, or a favorable plea agreement that minimizes the impact of their criminal charges. You can rely on us to seek the best possible outcome for you.</p>
